OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FWarm but
OL,6,Fcloudy during the evening, with spells
OL,7,Fof rain perhaps interspersed by some
OL,8,Fheavier and more showery bursts.
OL,9,FBecoming drier for a time during the
OL,10,Fearly hours.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FStaying rather cloudy, warm
OL,13,Fand humid, with further periods of
OL,14,Frain and some heavier and more showery
OL,15,Fdownpours possible.
